    "Our analysis revealed that the agent's thought process is particularly vulnerable, making this phase critical for reinforcing security.",
    "By prompting the agent to reassess the safety of its actions during thought generation, we sought to reduce the likelihood of malicious behavior emerging from different attacks.",
